  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "E-Commerce Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Order Fulfillment</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Pick, pack, and prepare orders accurately according to SOPs.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all packages are labeled and dispatched on time to meet delivery schedules.</li>\n  <li>Assist in handling returns, exchanges, and damaged goods.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Inventory &amp; Stock Management</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support in receiving, checking, and storing incoming stock.</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular stock counts and assist with inventory accuracy checks.</li>\n  <li>Report low stock levels, discrepancies, or damaged items to the supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Warehouse Operations</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness, organization, and safety of the warehouse area.</li>\n  <li>Operate basic warehouse equipment (e.g., barcode scanners, trolleys) safely.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Logistics &amp; Coordination</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Liaise with couriers and logistics partners for order collections and deliveries.</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparing shipping documents and ensuring compliance with delivery requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Team Support</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide support to the Warehouse Operations Manager and other team members.</li>\n  <li>Participate in training and development activities to improve work efficiency and achieve the KPIs set by Warehouse Operations Manager.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications &amp; Skills:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prior experience in warehouse, logistics, or e-commerce fulfillment is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with warehouse management systems (WMS) or barcode scanning tools preferred.</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and able to handle manual tasks such as lifting and moving goods.</li>\n  <li>Good organizational skills, attention to detail, and accuracy in work.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and meet tight deadlines.</li>\n  <li>Valid forklift license is preferred.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong><br>\nMon – Fri: 9AM-6PM, Sat: 9AM-1PM</p>\n<p>Overtime available (based on operational needs)</p>\n<p>Location : 18 Jalan Besut</p>",
