    "description": "<p>Established in 1968 and headquartered in Singapore, Alliance Global Distribution (formerly known as SUTL Corporation Pte Ltd) is one of Asia's foremost conglomerates with a presence in 18 countries across Asia and over 5,000 staff. Alliance Global Distribution has grown rapidly, riding on Singapore's expansive years as an entreport centre, leveraging on&nbsp;its entrepreneurial insights and knowledge, and building its reputation as a thriving company with unrivalled expertise in sales and trading.</p>\n<p>Today, Alliance Global Distribution is a partner to some of the best loved brands in the world to navigate through the region's complex and challenging market conditions.</p>\n<p>We also own-operate or own leisure &amp; lifestyle projects and&nbsp;retail concepts, like the prestigious ONE 15 Marina Club in Sentosa Cove.</p>",
